title: The Making Of The Rihanna Book

media:group.media:title: The Making Of The Rihanna Book
media:group.media:description: Step behind the scenes and take a look at the creation of the Rihanna book. Join Rihanna from the earliest meeting 5 years ago to the launch of the book at the Guggenheim Museum in New York City this past October. As a Valentine's Day gift to fans, the super-sized Luxury Supreme edition is available to order now on its own AND signed "Love, Rihanna" by Rihanna. Reserve your copy now at http://ri-hanna.io/rbook, Neiman Marcus, and Bergdorf Goodman.
